Introduction

BANDIT (Be Ambitious N Do It) , stylized as BVNDIT, was a 5-member girl group from MNH Entertainment, home to the soloist Chungha.

The line-up consists of Seungeun, Simyeong, Jungwoo, Songhee, and Yiyeon. The group debuted on April 2019 with the mini album BVNDIT, BE AMBITIOUS!

On November 11 2022, MNH Entertaintment released a statement regarding BVNDIT's contract that had ended on October 2022, thus leading to their disbandment.
